race.comment: HIT THE POST (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at Goulburn over 440m behind Gold Force (26.41) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at his previous run. His last run is a proven strong form reference. Ready to return to form. PRINCESS MIKA (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (18.90) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including three wins. Shapes as one to consider. CALLA OREO (7) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again. Something for the Multiples: SHE'S OUR JOY (5)
